{"tid":1976921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（玻狗抵撚死） 新加坡確診個案突破5000宗","createTime":"2020-04-17T14:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T03:47:12.000Z","uid":25240,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"f50e4327f43bc19a33d2c5c8da72488a3af60fe3","tid":1976921,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新加坡累計有超過5000宗，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新型冠狀病毒確診個案單日新增超過600宗</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡超過六成的感染者都是外籍勞工，外勞宿舍至少再出現五個新的感染群組。<br />\n<br />\n當局指，因應近日開始為大量外勞進行病毒檢測，確診病例飆升是預期之內，目前新加坡將7000名外勞隔離在18座臨時宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n由於外勞需要共用宿舍內的起居設施，加上供水不足的問題，浴室和廁所外往往大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n據報當局會再開放4座體育館讓外勞暫住，又正研究以兩艘郵輪安置部分康復和檢測呈陰性的外勞。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡政府本月初起停課和關閉非必要工作場所，日前又宣布民眾外出時必須要佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388095&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU91pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=89cae85e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388095&h=29a35a14\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388095</a>"},{"pid":"5d0774d927014edd32ca4e3f7c1176aaa2081baa","tid":1976921,"uid":80724,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"Errrrrr......"},{"pid":"4d0a095f37c3a8a7eda14f41aa118e8eeb1b2cb5","tid":1976921,"uid":43041,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"新加坡講得5000宗<br />\n<br />\n應該過50000<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b578ce8d83b474144f216d22ff6ee3109d5748a0","tid":1976921,"uid":283912,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"第一夫人又要叫春了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.